title: Add the location -58,106 to the Points of Interest
body:
> by 0x680ea404ac1201670c20d6b7d5bdbf4a934fa551 (CrystalLord)

## Parcel -58,106

![Parcel -58,106](https://api.decentraland.org/v1/parcels/-58/106/map.png)

Should the scene located at -58,106 be added to the Point of Interest list?

## Description

This land is designed to help new Ethermon players learn basic operations and practice skills.  I am an original Ethermon inhabitant in DCL and I am currently working closely with artists and game designers to create new Ethermon applications on DCL.

**[Vote on this proposal on the Decentraland DAO](https://governance.decentraland.org/en/proposal?id=0b318e50-bcbd-11eb-83da-d9722efc8034)**
author: 0x5E23D08324f017d5425e59A2782C9ae27aCE0958
